summary: THE VEHICLE WAS INVOLVED IN ACCIDENT, CONSUMER TOOK VEHICLE TO BE REPAIRED.  DEALERSHIP PRESENTED VEHICLE REPAIRS AS COMPLETE, CONSUMER DISAGREED.*MR  REAR GATE RELOCATED.   SWITCH CONTROLLING CARGO LAMP AND STATUS PANEL DID NOT FUNCTION.  FRONT BUMPER WAS GROSSLY MISALIGNED.  FRONT BUMPER TO RIGHT FRONT FENDER MISMATCHED.  REAR WIPER PIVOT COVER  WAS MISSING.  EXHAUST TIPS ROTATED.  BUMPER REINFORCEMENT BRACKETS WERE MISSING.  REAR TAIL LAMP SETTING OUT FROM BODY.  GATE HINGE BOLT FELL OUT.  INNER SKIRT WAS BOWED IN.  GAP IN RIGHT REAR DOOR.  VAPOR CANISTER IN THE ENGINE COMPARTMENT WAS LEFT LOOSE.  DRAIN HOSE NOT CONNECTED.  TIRE UNDER-INFLATED.   FLOOR DATUM POINTS LEFT UNDONE.   REAR HATCH OPENING WEATHERSTRIP WAS IMPROPERLY SEALED.    *TT  *JB
